<P ID="19">She was preceded in death by her parents; one daughter, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Patricia Shaw</ENAMEX>; one grandson, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Robert Michael Swails</ENAMEX>; one great-grandson, <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Jose Antonio Munoz Jr.</ENAMEX>; three brothers and two sisters.
